
<p>The objective is to form 4 programs from the given code snippets. 4 questions and 12 code snippets will be provided. The participant has to use the provided snippets and build the programs corresponding to each question. 3 snippets have to be used per question and each snippet can be used only in one question. These snippets provide only the essential logic behind the problem statements. The rest of the coding should be done by the participant. Participants can code in either C or C++ language. </p>